bubba-frontend (1.3.2) claire; urgency=low

  * Generic cleanup and removal of middle-pages
   - Printing
   - Services
   - System Backup/Restore
   - Date/Time
   - Software
  * Added FirePHP (default enabled at the moment) 
  * added initial jQuery-UI support 
  * removing old fwupdate view which hasn't been used for ages 

